{"tid":1866132,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"其實 支爆 已經幾可肯柒定會發生","createTime":"2020-02-06T14:34:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T15:14:44.000Z","uid":338879,"like":5,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"80af4b7d60707f403ead6959102b1ad38cb2d186","tid":1866132,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T14:34:45.000Z","msg":"大陸場疫症，無論係米中共有心制造出黎都好，好多野從結果都睇到大陸真係好唔撚掂<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1. 剛剛睇新聞，中海油作為國有油公司都唔買油<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200206/bkn-20200206161436377-0206_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200206%2Fbkn-20200206161436377-0206_00842_001.html&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=a2d717bd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200206/bkn-20200206161436377-0206_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n原因只有係唔夠錢，又或者啲油賣唔出，亦即係國內對油的需求大減，如果國家係發展緊向上，無可能會cut單<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n2. 中美貿易戰，中國根本買唔撚到咁多貨，個第一階段協議假到爆<br />\n<br />\n3. 國內一月二月經濟活動停鈍，今天GDP肯柒定收皮，分分鐘負增長，嘩，咁就大樂，失業潮破產倒閉潮黎，到時銀行收唔返大部份貸款，就hahahaha.. <br />\n<br />\n已經睇新聞連香港啲銀行都要跪低，只收息唔收本金，嘩，借錢出去收唔返！正！<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200206/bkn-20200206180650310-0206_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20200206%2Fbkn-20200206180650310-0206_00842_001.html&d=zpo3oWyV3xTDIRTZ1PVZWRphPZUtdHSu9roW7Om9%2Fes%3D&h=3476ed36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20200206/bkn-20200206180650310-0206_00842_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">拭目以待</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></strong>"},{"pid":"efc0bfc6457f801bb38964a3603923ca5a4b1b8e","tid":1866132,"uid":338879,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-06T14:41:22.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到<img